urdu transliteration text:
bolay padar se akbar barchi na khaynchnahai jaan ab labon par barchi na khaynchna
Akbar said to his father, don’t pull out the spear
@HujjatELC

maine tumhay bulaaya tha taake mai keh sakunbilkul na gham karo dil ko hai ab sukoonbaithe raho yahan magar barchi na khaynchna
Don’t pull out the spear
@HujjatELC

bolay hussain baap ko behla rahe hai aapmaloom hai ke yan se kahan ja rahe hai aapkehte ho moo ko phayr kar barchi na khaynchna
Don’t pull out the spear
@HujjatELC

saansein ukhad rahi to madham hai nafz bhikarte ho aah humko hai takeed sabr kikehte ho thaam ke jigar barchi na khaynchna
Don’t pull out the spear
@HujjatELC
